title: 35 - Monroe Martin III
itunes:title: 35 - Monroe Martin III
description: Happy New Year! Have we got a gift for you: it’s a killer new episode with Monroe Martin III. You’ve seen him on Fallon, Comedy Central, MTV, and a ton of other things, plus he’s got his own awesome podcast No Need for Apologies with Derek Gaines. We’re talking about everything from sports to rap to growing up in the foster care system. Here’s five words to describe this episode: get yourself home before curfew.
